    "title": "Looking for Hotel Manager at McDonald's India Consulting Pvt Ltd",
    "description": "Grow your career with McDonald's India Consulting Pvt Ltd! We are hiring a Hotel Manager for our Ahmedabad team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout McDonald's India Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nMcDonald's India Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with McDonald's India Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
